Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Card & Adventure Video Games: Monster Rancher Explorer Archive (Game Boy Color): Strategy: LEVEL 23

LEVEL 23

At the start of this stage,move 3 steps left.Create a box on your left and jump on it. Create another higher layer of box and jump on it. Nagas should be falling down now,when they are none of them,destroy the middile box,just below the key, and desrtoy the box left to it and the box on the metal ledge and jump on the metal ledge. At those "disc stone" pattern things that released the naga's,destroy the box undearneath it,so that the naga will fall below. With it desrtoyed you can climb your way up,but becareful about the naga's on the other side.
